{"title":"赞食堂","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞食堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食堂亮堂堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四壁有图画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方桌排成行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开会是会场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上课做课堂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱歌又跳舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人喜洋洋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体生活好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福万年长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去柴米油盐茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时时刻刻心牵挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产生活难管好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子过得乱如麻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在柴米油盐茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公共食堂来管家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产生活样样好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子甜得心开花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊　＊过去是：出门一把锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进门一把火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里里外外忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴都管不上！现在是：吃饭进食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活乐洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加紧忙生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身添力量！（江苏泰兴县刁铺人民公社社员）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}